org.codeoverflow.chatoverflow.api.plugin

Interface Pluggable


  • public interface Pluggable
    Pluggable is the entry point for chat overflow plugins. Should NEVER be changed! DO NOT UPDATE, REMOVE OR ADD ANYTHING TO THIS INTERFACE WITHOUT KNOWING WHAT YOU DOING! This interface is only there to provide some information about your plugin (most important: the api version).

      • createNewPluginInstance

        Plugin createNewPluginInstance(PluginManager manager)
        Returns the real chat overflow plugin. Should only be used after testing the api version number! If the plugin is not up-to-date, it might not be loaded due to possible reflection errors. Please do ONLY use the Plugin class to define your own chat overflow plugin logic! Create a new instance HERE every time!
        Parameters:
        manager - the manager implementation of the framework
        Returns:
        the plugin implementation of the plugin project, ready to get started!
